Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是沒有變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣生氣蓬勃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鴉 氣息都流過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從海那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增強射線的波動 你準備幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能光說別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幹的話就要確實把那傢伙殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會原諒那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易就背叛同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那麼注重同伴情誼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會想放那傢伙逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不相信我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不你來幹好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種男人 讓我來親手解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼喜歡鴉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的 不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 小鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鴉的決斷由我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也是這麼希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙我和鴉的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N  \N戰 \N \N \N \N鬥 \N \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到見面的時候 這附近的櫻花就會開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 禮物？ 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要能見到爸爸就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是好朋友 卻吵架了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生之間的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生之間啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打一次架的話 就會和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣 不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙也有女孩子的一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是舉個例子 舉個例子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 再和你聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著下周見面 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 我也去東京的中學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果要踢足球的話 還是東京比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一和老哥商量這事 一下就被吃了一拐子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼 我們家有那麼多錢麼 之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 如果要踢足球的話 是去義大利啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不對 是西班牙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不可能的啦 我可不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想告訴我 夢想和目的都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使去參加考試也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒有說過那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 你真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這樣不是很好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把合格作為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好兩人都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 上乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有看到鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 沒有看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就一直沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得要發生什麼事情似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能陪我一起找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 連一點線索都沒有就去找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那傢伙的消失那麼不安的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就安分地待在家裏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...再找找好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佑...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不必用那種口氣說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 讓我費那麼大功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們之間的遊戲...這就是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的好啊 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你說買什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買牌子不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不起床的話 要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 和你爸爸聯絡上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是被他說了什麼 關於離家出走的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為...這裏是你所選擇的虛幻的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是時間的流浪者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空的存在是無數的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一樣 擁有無數存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在其中 只有你一個擁有看見時空的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後根據你所看到的 來確定時空 來變成你的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說由於我看見了才變成現實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟 梟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也會變成現實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為我看見了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是知道些什麼告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在振動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空正在歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到那傢伙的悲鳴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會把我的樂趣讓給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從藤原那裏聽說了 鴉不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 還沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 好像很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我也看見了 黑披風的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑披風？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來幫忙找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在港口這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去山那邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是朋友嗎 不會放著你不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去彌生地方找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫上後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 再磨磨蹭蹭的就踢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不上車麼 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我的車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了還你鑰匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是中意這個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可不是絕對臨界組織計畫委員會的搜查了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田你也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有擲出骰子點數一的我 那麼在哪里也一定存在擲出六的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我想知道那個擲出六的我會變的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使擲出六也會是大失敗什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 薪金什麼的也能借到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙的痛苦可不止這麼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓遙的死白白浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空對我們來說只是幻影 為什麼你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒一點吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有時空的遙都和我們的遙聯繫著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我...要保護這個時空的遙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不會做的 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另...另一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是未來人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的角度來看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那傢伙是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意鴉的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我又沒有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好堅強啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然害怕卻不能逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是不同的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉還是鴉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能忍受下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要戰鬥到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼相信這個時空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間停止了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強啊 這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是未來 不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑和勇不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和未來的愛也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一直是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀 開始體表晶格化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人..一起給我消失吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摩爾擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs20}摩爾:物質量的表示單位 國際單位的基本單位之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏 這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟 他要發招了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀那傢伙消失逃走了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了時空收縮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 已經夠了 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要保護好遙啊 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會幫助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來 未來是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛 你 你一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰能來幫忙 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 藍色的雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個好像是飛向天空的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然變的悲傷起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想太多了 什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.91,0:25:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏日的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.81,0:25:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.40,0:25:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 給我抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.32,0:25:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰所決定好了的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.38,0:25:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對不會存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.73,0:25:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.88,0:25:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.97,0:25:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請將我的想法傳達給大家

